### Did this work in a previous version of Visual Studio and/or previous .NET release?

The DevExpress Report Designer works in .netframework just fine.

### Issue description

Created a report with the DevExpress Report Designer and opening up the report after it has already been created the designer hangs, then wipes out all the designer code for the controls on the report leaving it blank. 

I have checked with DevExpress and this is their response:

However, the loss of content on just opening a report is something we currently cannot explain or reproduce. It appears to be a severe bug that can potentially lead to significant loss of work.

